Code formatter:prettier, lint-staged, husky

ENV setup (.env at project root):

JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_here
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_oauth_client_id.apps.googleusercontent.com
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/yourdb

Auth routes:
- POST /login { mail, password }
- POST /register { userName, password, mail, name, phoneNumber, address }
- POST /auth/google { idToken }

Protected routes (Bearer token):
- PUT /me/profile { name?, phoneNumber?, address? }
- PUT /me/password { currentPassword, newPassword }
- POST /me/shipping-addresses { recipientName, phoneNumber, street, city, ... }

Google login (client): obtain ID token via Google Identity Services and send to /auth/google